data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Desirable Deep Creek pool home on a double lot with long greenspace views at the end of a short street cul-de-sac. Custom home with large Lanai, 4 Bedroom, flex room 4th bed/den/office with built-in cabinetry. This 4 bedroom, 2 Bath, boasts a split floorplan for family and guests to enjoy their privacy. Crown molding in main living areas for that stately grander look. Some rooms boast built-in's and a murphy wall bed. Oversized 2 car garage with storage/workshop area. New Roof 2023, HVAC 2022. Community area features Deep Creek golf course and Harbour Heights waterfront park with dock and boat ramp.
